Name: MPS Skudo Car Carrier
Description: MPS Skudo Car CarrierDuring car journeys it is important that your dog travels safely and comfortably. The Skudo Car carrier is ideal for those who want their dog to be comfortable in the car, thanks to its wide side entrance. It is made from light but strong plastic with ergonomic handles that make it easy to move. The fastener mechanism is external so that your dog will not be able to open it from the inside. This will ensure that your 4-legged friend will be safe especially when travelling. The large side and top openings guarantee sufficient air circulation.
